<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٠ - <span class="c2">(٥٢)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2102">وَزُهَيْرُ بْنُ حَرْبٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1132">جَرِيرٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> وَلَمْ يَذْكُرْ:</span> رَأْسُ الْكُفْرِ قِبَلَ الْمَشْرِقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>